verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
I'm not my own.
He purchased me.
I belong to you.
You belong to me.
We belong to Jesus,
The Christ of God,
And God is our God;
We've been made one in Him.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Yo no soy mío
sino soy comprado,
te pertenezco a tí,
me perteneces a mí,
Pertenecemos a Cristo
Cristo es de Dios
y Dios es nuestro
y somos uno en El.
